      <notesStmt>
        <note>Title from f. 13.</note>
        <note>Title and attribution according to New Catalogus Catalogorum: "Caṇḍī(stotra)prayoga(vidhi) by Nāgeśa Bhaṭṭa (or Nāgojī Bhaṭṭa); from his C. on Caṇḍīstotra or Devīmāhātmya."</note>
        <note>Listed by Poleman as Caṇḍīprayoga.</note>
        <note>Written 17-21 lines per leaf.</note>
        <note>Good condition.</note>
        <note>Orange powder rubbed in over some invocations, colophon, headings and other words. Some mistakes blocked out in black. A few marginal corrections.</note>
        <note>Begins: om̐ śrīgaṇeṣāya namaḥ om̐ namaścaṇḍikāyai athāsya saptasatīvyavahāraprayojaka saptasatahomavibhādarsita kātyāyanītantre mārkaṇḍeya ṛṣiḥ proktaḥ prathamaśloka.</note>
        <note>Ends: atra niṣkadakṣiṇāyāṁ daridrāṇāṁ catuḥsuvarṇam itarajatarūpaṁ dakṣiṇā sāṁarthānāṁ catuḥsuvarṇam iti hem.</note>
